<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Nicklas zu Sicheln, Kämmerer von Böhmen</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt, dass der vom Amtmann zu Totschnik gefangen genommene Konrad Weißenburger seit langem Bürger zu Nürnberg ist, und bittet um Unterstützung wegen seiner Freilassung und vollständige Herausgabe seiner Habe.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_68" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_68_r1l1">Dem <expan>Erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vveẏſen / Nyclaſen cʒum Sıcheln 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vve </del> <expan>etvven<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l2"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . des Künigs 
<del rend="strikethrough">von Beheim </del> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l3">Camrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> beſundern guten günner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1574321099276_213">Lieber 
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1574320884302_203">her </ab></add> Nẏclas / vns iſt fürbraht worden / vvie daʒ Jr dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l7">Chuncʒen weiſſemburger <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_r1l6">gen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>k<ex>ünig</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1574321168306_242">Beheim </ab></add></add> gar <expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l8">beholffen 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein wöllet </del> gevveſen ſeit / daʒ der von dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l9"><expan>Amptman<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒum Totſchenike der Jn gefangen hat / ledig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l10">werden ſülle / <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / ob wir euch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_line_1574321322730_289">C weıſſemburger <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſey 
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1576657953910_4365">des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1576657957502_4370">mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Alſo </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_line_1574321262547_259">vnd alſo </ab></add> laſſen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l14">wiſſen / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> C <expan>weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> yngeſeſſener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l15">vnd geſworner burger langcʒeit her gevveſen vnd noch iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l16"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr fürbaʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> aber darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l18">tun wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ledig <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_68_r1l17">mitſampt </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_line_1592288533448_354">
<add>ſeiner hab vngeſchacʒt</add> ledig werde / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_68_r1l20"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_68" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> weysen Nyclasen czum Sicheln,
                                <expan>etwen<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des
                        künigs, camrer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> besundern guten günner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <add>her</add> Nyclas, uns ist fürbraht worden, wie daz ir dem
                        Chunczen Weissemburger, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <add>gen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                            gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>k<ex>ünig</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>Beheim</add></add>, gar <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        beholffen gewesen seit, daz der von dem <expan>amptman<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        czum Totschenike, der in gefangen hat, ledig werden sülle,
                                <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ob wir euch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>huncz</ex></expan> Weissemburger <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> sey, <add>des wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                            fleisz <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan></add>; <add>und also</add> lassen
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>huncz</ex></expan>
<expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>ger</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> yngesessener und gesworner burger langczeit
                        her gewesen und noch ist. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir fürbaz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> aber darczu tun wöllet
                                <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <add>mitsampt</add>
<add>seiner hab ungeschaczt</add> ledig werde. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
